<a href="/articles/24699.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24699/indexMediumPc2/24699.jpg?1459314039" alt="「这世界」为了见前妻劫了飞机的事，你们都知道吧？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">「这世界」为了见前妻劫了飞机的事，你们都知道吧？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-30 13:44:25 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">4</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">35</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
